    <updated>2022-06-29T02:52:14.918Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">This video series explains the fundamentals of digital audio, how audio signals are expressed in the digital domain, how they&#39;re converted and transformed and the advantages of working with digital signals. We&#39;ll cover concepts of sampling theorem, sample rates, aliasing, bit depth, quantization, dither, pulse code modulation, sigma delta modulation, noise shaping and all that good stuff.</summary>
    
    
    
